---
title: Chicken, Cabbage and Apple Fricassee with Mashed Potatoes
description: All the elements in this dish are classics that are made for one another. Cabbage, apple and mustard have nothing but love for one another and couldn't pair better with a rich pan sauce and mash. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-cabbage-and-apple-fricassee-0e48fbd3.jpg
